      <title>吉尔丹任命前高盛高管为主席，以对抗维权投资者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/gildan-taps-ex-goldman-exec-as-chair-in-last-stand-against-activist-investor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大服装制造商 Gildan Activewear Inc. 表示，数名董事将在几天内离职，高盛集团 (Goldman Sachs Group Inc.) 的一名前高管将担任董事长，这是董事会为说服投资者不要支持激进股东的计划而做出的最后努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/gildan-taps-ex-goldman-exec-as-chair-in-last-stand-against-activist-investor</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 10:03:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
