      <title>英美资源集团反对赞比亚铅中毒案上诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/anglo-american-to-oppose-appeal-in-zambia-lead-poisoning-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英美资源集团表示，在原告被允许对之前的裁决提出上诉后，该公司将反对任何有关该公司持有股份的赞比亚矿山铅中毒数万人的指控的法庭案件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/anglo-american-to-oppose-appeal-in-zambia-lead-poisoning-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 09:44:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
